- **Export**: CSV download via `StringBuilder` + `File(bytes, "text/csv", ...)` — no extra library
- **Recommendations**: Simple rule-based text generation (no ML needed for MVP)

Stack: React 18 + TypeScript + Vite | ASP.NET Core 10 Web API | EF Core 10 | PostgreSQL (schema "horusvis")
